                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>At leisure is the Soul</l>
                    <l>That gets a staggering Blow - </l>
                    <l>The Width of Life - before it<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 spreads </l>
                    <l>Without a thing to do - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It begs you give it Work -</l>
                    <l>But just the placing Pins - </l>
                    <l>Or humblest Patchwork -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Children<add type="alternate" extent="do -">may -</add>
 do - </l>
                    <l>To<add type="alternate" extent="still it&#x27;s noisy Hands -">Help it&#x27;s Vacant Hands -</add>
 still it's noisy Hands - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
